  "prompt": "Can people see if you have viewed their instagram?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Instagram does not notify users when someone views their profile. However, Instagram does let users see who viewed their stories and highlights. When you post a story, you can swipe up to see a list of people who have viewed it. This feature is available for 24 hours while the story is active, or for as long as you keep it in your highlights. There are no built-in features on Instagram that allow users to see who has viewed their profile or individual posts.",
